<H3> <TI>   Bomb Discovered in RPP Election Headquarters </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA1903170594 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1600 
GMT 19 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1903170594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Text] A bomb placed in the Republican People's Party 
[RPP] election headquarters in Agri's Patnos District was 
discovered in time and rendered harmless. 
  According to information obtained by a Turkish Radio and 
Television correspondent, one person was seen entering the 
crowded election headquarters and placing the bomb. A member of 
the RPP picked up the bomb and threw it to an empty area. 
  Because of the explosion, several of the surrounding houses' 
windows were smashed. Nobody was injured in the incident. 

