<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Secret Launch"] </F>
  [Text] The disputed Eurofigther 2000 is finally taking 
off. The official date for its first flight is 15 April. As 
FOCUS has learned from a certain source, however, the 
multinational combat jet is to take off from the Manching 
factory of Deutsche Aerospace (Dasa) as early as the middle of 
