  [Text] France believes that the UN resolution condemning 
the Hebron massacre "should now be translated into effective 
measures." This declaration came in a statement made on Saturday 
[19 March] by French Foreign Ministry spokesman Richard Duque. 
  In the statement, France "welcomes" the adoption of the 
