Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ankara, Mar 21 (AA) -- Interior Minister Nahit 
Mentese said on Monday [21 March] that cooperation between 
Turkey and Iran against terrorists will continue and improve. 
  "We are sure that cooperation between Turkey and Iran that 
